{"tid":1619480,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"話俾大家《禁蒙面法》之下邊個可以戴口罩","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:18.000Z","uid":329986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6c92e5502e0be0ea8810ff77727b50ad56cfe9","tid":1619480,"uid":329986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>《禁止蒙面規條》第4條(3)(a)列明，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">法例不適用於</span></span>：</strong><br />\n<em>「該人當時身處有關集結、集會或有形，正在<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">從事某專業</span></span>或<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">受僱工作</span></span>，並於正在作出與該專頁或受僱工作相關的行為或活動時，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為了該人的人身安全，而使用有關蒙面物品</span></span>。」</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結論：<br />\n1）<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">哮喘患者（減少吸入今日的催淚煙，以免哮喘復發）</span></strong><br />\n2）其他人一律不能使用「口罩」保護自身安全！醫生、護士、急救人員都不會因為戴口罩而安全咗<br />\n3）但<span style=\"color: red;\">警察可蒙面（因為示威者很危險、威脅警務人員生命）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">據我所知香港有7百萬人患有哮喘，所以大家記得長期戴醫用口罩呀</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbcff17097188aa47cd276d12c37dcd1aa09a6f","tid":1619480,"uid":329986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"發漏咗圖片支持添<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A5hKZBV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA5hKZBV.jpg&h=8572bf7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFaD33B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFaD33B.jpg&h=bb461d6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b804347015cf512789487274c51be4e2106eed76","tid":1619480,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"FA可以喎"},{"pid":"fb62ddf302dbf9419c23ba2ed4850526abea8862","tid":1619480,"uid":303554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"注意：戴咗口罩<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔等於</span></strong></span>做到蒙面效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n部分人天真地以為用衛生理由戴口罩呢個合法豁免，就破解到蒙面法，但其實係跌入咗政府圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。試想想，之前後排嘅和理非可以合法地全身black bloc，先至能夠cover 到前線勇武手足，增加政府搜證困難：但而家即使後排嘅和理非戴咗口罩，客觀效果係喪失咗black bloc 嘅精義，變相isolate咗班前線。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2uEtzc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2uEtzc7.jpg&h=556be893&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}